## Context

* We use Shadcn/UI to style our application.

## Rules

- You must use Shadcn UI for components.
- You must use Tailwind CSS for styling (only if necessary on top of shadcn).

- You must install any ShadcnUI missing component with `pnpm dlx shadcn@canary add <component-name />`